Repo Structure

keralagovlinks/
├── public/
│   └── icons, favicon, etc.
├── src/
│   ├── components/       # Reusable UI elements
│   ├── pages/            # Next.js routing (or React views)
│   ├── data/             # JSON of verified links (initially static)
│   ├── utils/            # Helper functions (e.g., link checker)
│   └── styles/           # CSS / Tailwind config
├── .env.example          # API keys (if any)
├── README.md
├── CONTRIBUTING.md
├── LICENSE
├── package.json
└── next.config.js / vite.config.js / firebase.json


